    "subheading": "Fractional CFO engagements for U.S. businesses between $1M and $50M revenue &mdash; strategic finance, 13-week cash flow forecasting, board and investor reporting, fundraising support, and senior financial decision-making, delivered by experienced operators on a fixed monthly retainer. Limited engagements per quarter, accepted by application.",
    "actions": [
